  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study suggests that R-IDARAM combined with intrathecal immunochemotherapy may be high
      effective in primary central nervous system lymphoma (PCNSL) patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will evaluate response rate, progression free survival (PFS), overall
      survival (OS), and toxicity in primary central nervous system lymphoma (PCNSL) after systemic
      and intrathecal immunochemotherapy with deferred radiotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
